ios11.title: iOS Glyph
ios11.description: Apple introduced a new icon style for the tab bar icons. They are not thin outline icons anymore; these are the filled icons. Apple calls them the "glyphs."

android.title: Ice Cream
android.description: We suggest using Material Icons instead of this one, but hey, these are great too. You can also order some new icons in this style; just make sure you specify Android KitKat style explicitly when ordering.

win8.title: Windows Metro
win8.description: Icons8 started with this Windows 8 icons. Although we have created more icons in the newer Windows 10 style these days, you still can request us making some icons for it (please make sure you specify Windows 8 style explicitly when ordering).
